# SCHEMAS
**0.2.0** Restructured form to include both basic and full form: mandatory questions (i.e. basic form) based off of Wildlabs's The Inventory schema, remaining questions (i.e. full form) restructured in separate sections, all optional so far; circa 6702825

**0.1.0** Untracked, translating Google Forms-based questionnaire into JSON-based schema (after code redesign, version >1.0.0)

**0.0.0** Untracked, based off of Graham's initial set of questions during STSM in Aarhus

